\section{Purchasing and renting}
\label{sec:purchasing_and_renting}
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%

Many aspects of purchasing or renting a residence
have sustainability implications, size and location chief among them.


